42:03.521 --> 42:05.323
Where the hell you been?

42:12.463 --> 42:14.199
I-I know I can't
be getting a write-up

42:14.299 --> 42:16.568
so close to my parole hearing.

42:16.668 --> 42:20.505
Ah, Bode, I'm afraid
this offense

42:20.606 --> 42:22.674
is a little more severe
than just a write-up.

42:22.774 --> 42:24.810
For breaking curfew?

